data.description: This 2-story propertyis inviting you to feel right at home. The interior is highlighted by a spacious great room along with wood-look flooring is perfect for relaxing and entertaining. Kitchen is a cook's delight, featuring ample cabinetry, SS appliances, granite counters, a convenient pantry, and a center island with a breakfast bar. Versatile loft space is ideal for use as a game or entertainment area. The main bedroom is a serene retreat, boasting a walk-in closet and a private bathroom with dual sinks. Delightful backyard is complete with a covered patio, a seating area, a rejuvenating hot tub, and low-maintenance artificial turf. You'll enjoy access to the community's pool, spa, and more. This property is a true gem, offering the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience!
